data.description:
Motivated seller, submit your best offer!

Condo is being sold as-is.  

AC evaporator coil needs to be replaced!
  
FHA Approved, 2 bedroom, 1 1/2 bath, condo is in a gated community and has a community pool. 

The kitchen features a new Amana Stainless Steel stove, microwave, and refrigerator.  There's upgraded ceiling fans, light fixtures, and Oxford Brindle Oak Waterproof Luxury Vinyl flooring throughout.  Dual vanities with lots of storage in the full bath and both rooms have large closets.  The washer and dryer convey.

Imagine starting and ending your day on your covered, screened in patio with extra storage space.  This condo is in the heart of Jacksonville and close to Saint John's Town Center and Mayport Naval Station.

Don't delay, schedule your appointment today!
